=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">e</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">self</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/StructureGroupoid.html#StructureGroupoid.members\">members</a></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">e'</span> <a href=\"./Init/Core.html#HasEquiv.Equiv\">≈</a> <span class=\"fn\">e</span> → <span class=\"fn\">e'</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Membership.mem\">∈</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">self</span>.<a href=\"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/StructureGroupoid.html#StructureGroupoid.members\">members</a></span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Membership in a structure groupoid respects the equivalence of open partial homeomorphisms. ","docLink":"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/StructureGroupoid.html#StructureGroupoid.mem_of_eqOnSource'","kind":"theorem","line":101,"name":"StructureGroupoid.mem_of_eqOnSource'","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/StructureGroupoid.lean#L101-L101"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Geometry/Manifold/StructureGroupoid.html#StructureGroupoid.locality'\"><span class=\"name\">StructureGroupoid</span>.<span class=\"name\">locality'</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">H</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Topology/Defs/Basic.html#TopologicalSpace\">TopologicalSpace</a> <span class=\"fn\">H</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Math